      <title>好斗的LE笔希望通过法国的选举禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/a-combative-le-pen-looks-to-move-past-france-s-election-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的极右翼国家拉力赛承认法院裁定造成的损害范围，禁止其领导人Marine Le Pen竞选选举。但是该党坚持认为这场战斗还没有结束，它将试图利用争议来发挥其优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/a-combative-le-pen-looks-to-move-past-france-s-election-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 14:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
