      <title>策略的Trennert在健康问题上退出了财政部工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trennert-of-strategas-pulls-out-of-treasury-job-on-health-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博新闻社对客户的声明，Strategas Securities共同创始人Jason de Sena Trennert不再在竞选中成为美国财政部助理秘书，这是由于新发现的健康问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trennert-of-strategas-pulls-out-of-treasury-job-on-health-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 13:52:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
