    <item>
      <title>美国卫生机构开始大规模裁员，因为小rfk订购了10,000个工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-health-agency-mass-firings-begin-as-kennedy-orders-10-000-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社报道的一份备忘录，美国卫生和公共服务部开始于周二清晨解雇工人，包括涉及毒品和烟草安全的最高监管机构，因为秘书罗伯特·肯尼迪（Robert F. Kennedy Jr.]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-health-agency-mass-firings-begin-as-kennedy-orders-10-000-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 12:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
